      <title>也门附近油轮上的武装警卫与船只交火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/red-sea-tanker-guards-exchange-fire-with-small-boat-near-yemen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘油轮上的武装警卫在红海与一艘小船交火，这是世界上最危险的水道之一的担忧不断升级的另一个迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/red-sea-tanker-guards-exchange-fire-with-small-boat-near-yemen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西南航空的小幅前景令华尔街失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/southwest-air-lifts-revenue-guidance-on-holiday-travel-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管假期旅行强于预期，但西南航空仍基本保持年终前景不变，这令原本预计会有更大提振的投资者感到不安。]]></description>
